<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style type="text/css">
    body,
    p,
    div,
    pre {
      font-family: 'Inter', 'Lato', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      font-family: Inter;
      font-style: normal;
      font-weight: normal;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 24px;
    }

    a {
      color: #df405d !important;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    a:hover {
      color: #df405d !important;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    pre {
      background-color: whitesmoke;
      color: #4a4a4a;
      overflow-x: auto;
      padding: 1rem 1rem;
      white-space: pre;
      word-wrap: normal;
    }

    p {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      margin: 0 auto;
      max-width: 600px;
    }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <p>
        Hi!<br/><br/>

        The username association with this email is {{username}}<br /><br />

        If you need to reset your password, go ahead and follow this link:<br /><br />
        <a style="color: #df405d" href="{{siteUrl}}/resetpassword?email={{email}}&token={{token}}">Reset Your Password</a><br /><br />

        Just a heads up, to make sure your information is safe and secure, the above link will expire after 24 hours.<br /><br />

        If you didn't request a password change, then just ignore this message.<br /><br />

        Best Regards<br />
        ---<br />
        OpenSquare Team
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
